defs.name: NoHashHasher
defs.docs:
For an enabled type `T`, a `NoHashHasher<T>` implements `std::hash::Hasher` and
 uses the value set by one of the `write_{u8, u16, u32, u64, usize, i8, i16, i32,
 i64, isize}` methods as its hash output.
